==階段一==
F-X第一階段始於2002年，目的在於更換老舊的[[F-5|F-5]]戰鬥機，主要目標還是以外購現成戰機為主，入選的有[[颱風戰機|颱風戰機]]和[[F-15K|F-15K]]、[[Su-35|Su-35]]。最終於F-15K得標。
==階段二==
2007年提出的第二階段為升級專案，將F-15K的發動機升級為F100-PW-229EEP。
==階段三==
2014年提出的第三階段是要淘汰老舊的[[F-4|F-4]]E戰機取得新的多用途戰機，原本意圖取得[[F-22|F-22]]然而美國禁止出口，所以[[F-15SE|F-15SE]]、F-35和[[T-50|T-50]]列入考慮，瑞典也表示願意推出一種[[JAS-39|JAS-39]]的變型版本角逐。預算為73億美金購買60架，最終較有可能購買F-35。<ref>Mundy, Simon; Jung-a, Song (22 November 2013). "South Korea agrees Lockheed stealth fighter jets deal". ft.com. The Financial Times Ltd. Retrieved 22 November 2013.</ref>最終於F-35A得標。<ref>[http://www.lockheedmartin.com/us/news/press-releases/2014/september/0924-aero-south-korea-f-35.html Republic Of Korea Approves Procurement Of Lockheed Martin F-35A Lightning II] {{Webarchive|url=https://archive.today/20140924195732/http://www.lockheedmartin.com/us/news/press-releases/2014/september/0924-aero-south-korea-f-35.html |date=2014-09-24 }} - Lockheed news release, 24 September 2014</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=https://thediplomat.com/2017/12/south-korea-moves-forward-with-plans-to-buy-20-more-f-35-stealth-fighter-jets/ |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2020-07-01 |archive-date=2019-07-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190715152340/https://thediplomat.com/2017/12/south-korea-moves-forward-with-plans-to-buy-20-more-f-35-stealth-fighter-jets/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

